This is your sanity bar. It fills when enemies reach your CPU. Do not let it fill unless you wanna become cyberpsycho
This is your temperature bar. Placing a new defense makes it go up. Removing defenses make it go down over time. Moving defences bumps it up slightly
This is a condensator. It can hold off the enemy signal for some time before they overwhelm it
This is a coil - it slows enemies down
This is a diode - it halves the signal that passes through it
You can always pause the game and take a moment to think, just hit space